{
  "texts": [
    "In order to empirically investigate the relative importance of each component in an MC question, various input formats are trialled in the question complexity system.",
    "Table 1 presents different combinations of the context, question and answer options where one or more components have been omitted from the standard (full) input format.",
    "Each input is prepended with the [CLS] token and each component is separated by the [SEP] token.",
    "standard c + q + oA + oB + oC + oD context c context-question c + q question-option q + oA + oB + oC + oD",
    "Table 1: Input formats for the complexity system."
  ]
}